				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hmm a prepaired mage can counter many necro strategys.(as can anyone really). Fight in an arena so you can dispell your pet.<br><br>Necro fears/roots/darkness/st mage pet. Dispel mage pet and fears/roots/darkness/st gone. Leave first buff slot on pet open to make this easy or don't buff pet.<br><br>Necro dots mage. Mage dispells or cures dot(cure disease and poisen potions)<br><br>Necro roots/darkness/ST mage. Mage will resists due to MR. Pet can be dispelled to remove root/darkenss/ST<br><br>Necro has sow/run3 to outrun your pet-&gt;sow pet(potion) and dispell necro.<br><br>The weeknesses are the following. Mage needs to either nuke necro or kill him with pet. Necro can resist mage nukes with MR+FR equipment. Mala might not be enough to make him hitable. The necro may be able to out run magepet with run3.<br><br>silfe xev <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/usilfe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Silfe</A> at: 3/19/02 5:47:41 pm<br></i></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
